{"tid":2373290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"走投無路 旅巴司機賣眼求活","createTime":"2021-01-20T10:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T11:11:03.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5a142714ad3f313f5b45efba246bb7b06968f3","tid":2373290,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.udnbkk.com/data/attachment/portal/202101/19/190826cokdk80d9wtt3k07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.udnbkk.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fportal%2F202101%2F19%2F190826cokdk80d9wtt3k07.jpg&h=869aae23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【編譯單亦霆／曼谷報導】新冠肺炎疫情重挫旅遊業，普吉府某旅行社的長途巴士司機塔威（60歲）在失去收入來源後，為了能夠支撐家裡開銷，繳付孫子下一個學期的學費，竟不惜在網上發佈「出售一隻眼睛」的告示，希望藉此解決家裡的財務問題。<br />\n<br />\n塔威接受媒體採訪時表示，平常家裡就只有他、妻子麗娜和孫子，3人共同租住在鄰居哥威（38歲）的房子，孫子就讀高中二年級，學業非常優秀，而且很孝順夫婦倆，立志考公務員，說要回饋他們的養育照顧之恩。<br />\n<br />\n從去年開始有了新冠肺炎疫情，國內旅遊業受到嚴重打擊，僱用自己的旅行社也受到影響，他偶爾才被分派到工作，所以收入也隨之減少，最後他連每個月5000銖房租都負擔不起，所幸哥威不計較，他只好每次繳付1000-2000銖，以暫時解決租金問題。<br />\n<br />\n哥威表示，他在聽到塔威要賣一隻眼睛時，被他的瘋狂行為嚇了一跳，雖然他沒有能力給塔威一家太多幫助，但也會提供一些食物給他們一家三口，同時免除他們部分房租租金，希望能夠舒緩他們的困境，大家一起度過難關。<br />\n<br />\n麗娜和孫子說，兩人對於塔威賣眼睛的決定感到相當無奈，但他們確實沒有能力賺錢，所以也不知如何是好。<br />\n<br />\n塔威說，自己也是走投無路了，他知道這樣做是很錯誤的選擇，但也是被逼無奈，不知道能依靠誰，不然怎會賣自己的一隻眼睛？<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當地相關部門已經前往查看塔威家庭實況，並且準備給他們一家提供援助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.udnbkk.com/portal.php?mod=view&amp;aid=311426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.udnbkk.com%2Fportal.php%3Fmod%3Dview%26aid%3D311426&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=af5178d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.udnbkk.com/portal.php?mod=view&amp;aid=311426</a>"},{"pid":"23df505754f01ff0c0d9fa6c749f3220405b0f9c","tid":2373290,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3f9b011d8422a8a4dac93c24cbc61c66fa6e9f","tid":2373290,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"23df505754f01ff0c0d9fa6c749f3220405b0f9c","tid":2373290,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"條友深黃"},{"pid":"214cd6b65808e9f78fbc7c1e78bd76fc2995b607","tid":2373290,"uid":311626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"煲湯？"},{"pid":"f2ef2343ce6e373722003b3f57fdeb706bcf4eea","tid":2373290,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:01:19.000Z","msg":"唔賣賢？"},{"pid":"54ac28ec450d55c31c32f30469e94152bb320942","tid":2373290,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2ef2343ce6e373722003b3f57fdeb706bcf4eea","tid":2373290,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:01:19.000Z","msg":"唔賣賢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"驚得罪心跳狗"},{"pid":"d5494d4b0e9ee5c43c2419bfee21120da3568424","tid":2373290,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54ac28ec450d55c31c32f30469e94152bb320942","tid":2373290,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2ef2343ce6e373722003b3f57fdeb706bcf4eea","tid":2373290,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:01:19.000Z","msg":"唔賣賢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"驚得罪心跳狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />关咩事"}]}